Election times in Kenya are political marvels to watch and 2017 stands way above the rest in terms of generating drama. It is a year of many political ups and downs, moments of exhilaration as well as of gloom. While many politicians have influence on selected crowds, one is an unusual constant in Kenya’s political gyrations and has magnetic control over his true believers. Although he does not hold any elected office, Raila Odinga is seemingly so gifted with high capacity for creating national anxiety that he appears to be untouchable.
 Subterfuge 
